4	Classes:
5	  - MapBridge        — QObject exposed to JavaScript via QWebChannel
6	  - RadarMapWidget   — QWidget wrapping QWebEngineView with Leaflet map
7	
8	The full HTML/CSS/JS for Leaflet is generated inline (no external files).
9	Supports: OSM, Google, Google Sat, Google Hybrid, ESRI Sat tile servers;
10	coverage circle, target trails, velocity-based color coding, popups, legend.
11	"""
